<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A9204006001">
<title>
Scan Tool Data Definitions
</title>
<topic id = "AENBP70A9204006002">
<title>
Battery Voltage (V):
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates battery voltage inputted from IG1 relay to headlight auto leveling and washer control module.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENBP70A9204006003">
<title>
Leveling Actuator (%):
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates in percent how much correction is needed in headlight leveling actuators so that headlight auto leveling and washer control module maintains a proper optical axis of headlights based on signals inputted from rear vehicle height sensor. 
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENBP70A9204006004">
<title>
Rear Height Sensor (mV):
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates the input signal from rear vehicle height sensor.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENBP70A9204006005">
<title>
Vehicle Speed (km/h, mph):
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates the vehicle speed calculated ECM.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENBP70A9204006006">
<title>
Headlight Switch (ON/OFF):
</title>
<ptxt>
This indicates state of lighting switch.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
ON: Lighting switch is in “ON” position and headlights are on.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
OFF: Lighting switch is in clearance light, “OFF” position and headlights are off.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</topic>
</servinfosub>
